<br>
The fact is, Verant made healing so efficient and melee so effective that this combination could theoretically kill anything in the game.  Unlike mana which is very inefficiently 'healed,' and magic damage - which is not nearly as efficient as healing -  melee damage is infinite.  There's absolutely nothing stopping the tank from doing damage for eternity except the amount of hit points that tank has.<br>
<br>
Should healing be less efficient?  I wouldn't go that way, but I DO think Verant should reconsider the way they have been with magic damage and mana. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utorridbrightflame.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Torrid BrightFlame</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/8/02 3:22:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=648.topic&index=163>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~torrid/torrs2.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mana and healing</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  Your point being? You can kill pretty much any uber MOB without rogues too, but you don't see many guilds doing it. Most of the top-tier guilds have many active wizards because guilds recognize the power they bring to a raid-type setting.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Uhm I made my point very clear.  Someone called wizards &quot;critical&quot; to raids.  I can't imagine canceling ANY raids for lack of wizards, save hate, air, and gore/hoshkar if you are low on people.  My guild has 3 ex-60 bane wizards that completely stopped playing their wizards to play monks, and two lower 50s wizards that now play a warrior/monk.  There is no doubt my guild is the better for it.  Mainly because they pull for us though :P  Every single ex-60 bane wiz in my guild concluded that their monks contribute more to the raid than if they played their wizards, even when not pulling.  I would have been a 4th ex-60 wiz, but I play both of my characters simultaneously.<br>
<br>
Sure wizards are great on bane mobs.  Are wizards critical in killing them?  I don't think so.  My guild decided to value rogues and monks higher when we were recruiting because those two classes will help kill the &quot;trash&quot; faster, will perform better on non-bane mobs (usually), and don't eat from the guild fund for pdots.<br>
<br>
Isn't anyone else mad about the pdots?! :P<br>
<br>
Well thats the opinions/observations of my guild and myself anyway.  If you want to flame me for my opinions, be my guest.<br>
<br>
